      <guid>/posts/twemoji-support/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want to use Twitter&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a href=&#34;https://twemoji.twitter.com/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Twemoji&lt;/a&gt; across your website, enable it in your &lt;code&gt;config.toml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e5e5e5;background-color:#000;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[params]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  enableTwemoji = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This will not only give your website unified emojis across all platforms. It will also give you &lt;a href=&#34;https://blog.emojipedia.org/twemoji-13-0-emoji-changelog/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;the latest Unicode 13 emoji set&lt;/a&gt;, such as ðŸ§‹ðŸ«•ðŸ›»ðŸª—ðŸªž.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size-&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size-&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--1&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--1&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--2&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--2&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--3&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--4&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--4&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;h6 id=&#34;emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--5&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Emoji size changes with text size ðŸ¤©&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#emoji-size-changes-with-text-size--5&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h6&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;</description>
