    <item>
      <title>Render LaTeX using KaTeX</title>
      <link>/posts/render-latex-using-katex/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/posts/render-latex-using-katex/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Enable katex by adding &lt;code&gt;katex = &amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt; to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/content-management/front-matter/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;front matter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e5e5e5;background-color:#000;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f00&#34;&gt;+++&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;katex = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0ff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;true&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f00&#34;&gt;+++&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to enable KaTeX or MathJax for all post, add &lt;code&gt;katex = ture&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;math = true&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;config.toml&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;[params]&lt;/code&gt; section.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s almost a dropin alternative to the mathjax solution,you should just choose one of them.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Inline math looks like this&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e5e5e5;background-color:#000;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-tex&#34; data-lang=&#34;tex&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is text with inline math &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0ff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;\sum&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;_{n&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff0;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;}^{&lt;/span&gt;\infty&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;} &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff0;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;^{&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;n} &lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff0;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0ff;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is text with inline math $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} 2^{-n} = 1$&lt;br&gt;&#xA;and with math blocks:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
